iculture and Forestry of T\u00fcrkiye, and Ministry of Finance and Economy of Turkmenistan); United Nations Resident Coordinator Offices and United Nations Country Teams (OHCHR Cambodia, UNDP Indonesia, FAO Lao People\u2019s Democratic Republic, FAO Vanuatu, IOM Turkey); Eurasian Development Bank; USAID and Mars Inc. in Indonesia; Delegation of the European Union to Indonesia; TONIBUNG in Malaysia; Society Roots for Equity and Pakistan Kissan Mazdoor Tehreek (PKMT) in Pakistan; and Singapore Agri- Food Innovation Lab kindly shared cases or examples of country-level innovative approaches, solutions and good practices to energy, food and finance to be considered for the report, directly or through web-based survey responses. Research and data support was provided by: Kayla Shelby Kingseed, Gabriela Ana Cestino Lopez, and Jinyu Ling (ESCAP); Dave Pipon (ADB); and Raymond Gaspar (UNDP). Acknowledgements iv Delivering on the Sustainable Development Goals through Solutions at the Energy, Food and Finance Nexus Tom Felix Joehnk edited the manuscript, and project administration support was provided by Aqira Bhatchayutmaytri. Communications and publishing support was provided by Symone Marie Mccollin-Norris, Mitch M. Hsieh, Raggie Johansen and Kavita Sukanandan (ESCAP); Mercedes Martin (ADB); Mahtab Haider (UNDP); the Publications Board of the United Nations, Office of the Executive Secretary, ESCAP; ADB Corporate Services Department; and the publishing team of ADB\u2019s Department of Communications. Publication design and layout was by Xiao Dong and Qi Yin with support from Charlene L. Claret of ADB.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "045efd0e-9518-4363-bf9c-e408f90af180": {"__data__": {"id_": "045efd0e-9518-4363-bf9c-e408f90af180", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/del