ultural productivity and livelihoods and have severe effects on supply chains. Key commodity prices, consumer price inflation, and market uncertainty remain elevated. The Russian invasion of Ukraine has severely exposed some 38", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "407e6205-0c4a-4870-a6e5-12df757c2ffd": {"__data__": {"id_": "407e6205-0c4a-4870-a6e5-12df757c2ffd", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/delivering-sustainable-development-goals-through-solutions-energy-food-and-finance-nexus-2023-asia-pacific-sdg-partnership", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Delivering on the Sustainable Development Goals through Solutions at the Energy, Food and Finance Nexus: 2023 Asia-Pacific SDG Partnership Report", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/delivering-sustainable-development-goals-through-solutions-energy-food-and-finance-nexus-2023-asia-pacific-sdg-partnership", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "0fc7b58cbdc8a1d6a32f4fee1d27c2bd413e2353b3a43af2e08da97f4facd0ee"}, "3": {"node_id": "14cee602-0250-4921-a473-71a14c89339f", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/delivering-sustainable-development-goals-through-solutions-energy-food-and-finance-nexus-2023-asia-pacific-sdg-partnership", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "1300aa06539e1bd5c7d8e9914b13945966859f06c93dcc8fffd5a213ab810bbe"}}, "ha